<p class="contextTtl" id="p1" data-pid="1"><span id="page37" class="pageNum" aria-hidden="true" data-no="37" data-before-text="37"></span><strong>レッスン09</strong></p>
<h1 id="p2" data-pid="2"><strong>祈ることによって神との友情を育てる</strong></h1>
</header>	<div class="clearfix alternatePresentation clickable noTooltips
		">
		<div class="thumbnail">
